These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, water, almond-milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, jazz, rock
1. the fan of jazz is the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the fan of rock and the person drinking water##2
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | water | almond-milk | cola |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | metal    | rock   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, video-games, writing
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, software-developer
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the software-developer is between the bartender and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | cooking    | writing        | video-games |
| Job     | doctor | software-developer | bartender         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, soy-milk
3 different pets are kept: lizard, snake, mouse
1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking fanta is between the owner of the snake and the person drinking soy-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | lemonade | fanta     | soy-milk |
| Pet        | snake  | mouse | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, trance, classical
3 different pets are kept: turtle, goat, hamster
1. the fan of punk is the owner of the turtle##1
2. the fan of classical is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the turtle##2
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | classical     | punk |
| Pet           | goat | hamster | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, card-games
3 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, bird
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | hiking | card-games     | gardening |
| Pet     | bird    | dog | hamster    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, italian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, rugby, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the italian and the canadian##2
2. the canadian is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the colombian is on the right of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | canadian  | colombian   | italian        |
| Sport         | rugby | sailing | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: pepper, corn, avocado
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, indonesian, spanish
1. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
2. the nigerian is between the person eating avocado and the indonesian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | corn  | pepper  | avocado |
| Nationality   | indonesian | nigerian | spanish     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, drama, musical
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, malaysian, spanish
1. the person watching drama movies is the spanish##1
2. the malaysian is between the person watching drama movies and the person watching musical movies##2
3. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | mystery  | drama  |
| Nationality   | japanese | malaysian | spanish |

