.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, sailing, rugby
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, taxi, airplane
1. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person driving the van is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person driving the taxi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | rugby | cricket | sailing  |
| Transport   | airplane    | van        | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
