The people use 3 different means of transport: van, train, ship
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the chef##1
2. the designer is between the person driving the ship and the police-officer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Job         | chef | designer | police-officer |
| Transport   | ship     | van    | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, apple, lime
1. the person eating lime is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person eating pineapple##2
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | sprite      | iced-tea      |
| Food       | apple  | lime | pineapple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
