The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, basketball, soccer
1. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is basketball##2
3. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | techno   | soul   |
| Sport         | basketball | soccer | cycling |

