2. the dutch is on the far left##1
3. the dutch is the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | dutch | french   | canadian   |
| Sport         | swimming  | snowboarding | badminton |

