.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, 7up
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, metal, house
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking 7up and the fan of metal##2
3. the fan of pop is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | 7up | mirinda   | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | house  | pop | metal   |

 